# 📱 StudXchange – College Marketplace App

A modern Flutter-based marketplace app designed for college students to buy and sell items within campus.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🛒 Buy & Sell Items
- 🔍 Smart Item Discovery
- ❤️ Wishlist System
- 🔔 Real-time Notifications
- 💬 Chat between Buyer & Seller
- 💸 Booking / Order System
- ⭐ Reviews & Ratings
- 📊 Smart Recommendations
- 🎨 Premium UI (Dark + Light Mode)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Flutter (Frontend)
- Firebase Firestore (Database)
- Firebase Auth (Authentication)
- Firebase Storage (Images)
- Git & GitHub (Version Control)

